'''瓦杜茨城堡'''（{{lang-de|'''Schloß Vaduz'''}}）是[[列支敦士登親王|列支敦士登親王]]的官方居住地<ref name=o>{{cite web |url=http://www.gowealthy.com/gowealthy/wcms/en/home/articles/travel/sightseeing/Vaduz-Castle-Liechtenstein-JPhKgKrA1x.html |title=Sightseeing : Vaduz Castle- Liechtenstein |publisher=Gowealthy.com |date= |accessdate=2012-06-20 |archive-date=2012-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121008082437/http://www.gowealthy.com/gowealthy/wcms/en/home/articles/travel/sightseeing/Vaduz-Castle-Liechtenstein-JPhKgKrA1x.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。城堡位于[[列支敦士登|列支敦士登]]首都[[瓦杜茨|瓦杜茨]]附近的山顶上<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.virtualtourist.com/travel/Europe/Liechtenstein/Vaduz/Things_To_Do-Vaduz-MISC-BR-1.html |title=Fun Things To Do in Vaduz - Attractions & Must See |publisher=VirtualTourist |date= |accessdate=2012-06-20 |archive-date=2017-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801001033/http://www.virtualtourist.com/travel/Europe/Liechtenstein/Vaduz/Things_To_Do-Vaduz-MISC-BR-1.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://tourismus.li/en/lie/place/Vaduz%20Castle/ |title=Principality of Liechtenstein: Travel, holidays, vacations - Activities - Popular sights & the countryside: Vaduz Castle |date=31 March 2018 |accessdate=31 March 2018 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203104833/https://tourismus.li/en/lie/place/Vaduz%20Castle/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
。

==历史==
之前的拥有者可能是韦登伯格-萨根斯家族，也就是这个城堡的建造者。这个城堡的主塔(建于12世纪)和东部部分地区是最古老的。该塔位于一块面积为{{convert|12|x|13|m|0|abbr=off}}的地面上。在底层，塔墙的厚度可达{{convert|4|m|0|abbr=off}}。原入口位于庭院一侧，高{{convert|11|m|0|abbr=off}}。圣安娜教堂大概也建于中世纪。主祭坛是新哥特式的。在1499年的斯瓦比亚战争中，这座城堡被瑞士邦联烧毁。西侧由卡斯帕·冯·赫内姆斯伯爵(1613-1640)扩建。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tourismus.li/en/culture-cuisine/places-of-cultural-interest/cultural-places-of-historical-interest/Vaduz-Castle.html |title=Liechtenstein : The Official Tourism Site - Culture & Cuisine - Places of historical interest : Vaduz Castle |date=2013-01-05 |accessdate=2013-01-05 |archive-date=2013-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507072907/http://www.tourismus.li/en/culture-cuisine/places-of-cultural-interest/cultural-places-of-historical-interest/Vaduz-Castle.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author=Cornelia Herrmann |chapter=Die Kunstdenkmäler des Fürstentums Liechtenstein. Das Oberland|title=Gesellschaft für Schweizerische Kunstgeschichte GSK: ''Die Kunstdenkmäler der Schweiz''|location=Bern|year=2007|isbn=978-3-906131-85-6 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.burgenwelt.org/liechtenstein/vaduz/object.php |title=Vaduz Castle on Burgenwelt.de (in German) |date=2016-01-22 |accessdate=2016-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422031127/http://www.burgenwelt.org/liechtenstein/vaduz/object.php |archive-date=2019-04-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.burgenwelt.org/liechtenstein/vaduz/object.php#grundriss |title=Ground plan of Vaduz Castle on Burgenwelt.de (in German) |date=2016-01-22 |accessdate=2016-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422031127/http://www.burgenwelt.org/liechtenstein/vaduz/object.php#grundriss |archive-date=2019-04-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

列支敦士登的王族于1712年买下了瓦杜兹城堡，买下了瓦杜兹伯爵爵位。此时，神圣罗马帝国皇帝查尔斯六世将1699年由列支敦士登购买的谢伦堡伯爵爵位与贵族爵位合并，形成了现在的列支敦士登公国。

==今日==
城堡在1905年至1920年间经过一次大修缮，此后于20年代初在[[约翰二世_(列支敦士登)|约翰二世]]主持下又经历一次修缮，并于30年代初由[[弗朗茨·约瑟夫二世_(列支敦士登)|弗朗茨·约瑟夫二世]]主持扩建。自1938年起，该城堡便是列支敦士登大公家庭的主要居住地。大公家庭现今仍居住于城堡中，故城堡不对外开放<ref>{{cite web |url=http://merlinandrebecca.blogspot.com/2011/08/castle-hunting-schloss-valduz.html |title=Article about Vaduz Castle and Schalun castle (includes images of both) |date=2011-08-18 |accessdate=2013-04-14 |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206011930/http://merlinandrebecca.blogspot.com/2011/08/castle-hunting-schloss-valduz.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tourismus.li/en/navpage-CultureLI-HistoricalSightsLI-142905.html |title=Liechtenstein - Vaduz Castle |publisher=Tourismus.li |date= |accessdate=2012-06-20 |archive-date=2012-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120807152014/http://www.tourismus.li/en/navpage-CultureLI-HistoricalSightsLI-142905.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ruinenland.de/burgen-luxemburg.htm |title=Photo gallery of Liechtenstein and Luxembourg castles, including photos of Vaduz Castle |date=2011-08-18 |accessdate=2013-04-14 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116074406/http://www.ruinenland.de/burgen-luxemburg.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

